query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.info in ('LD video artifacts','LD dynamic range','sound mix','adaption','LD audio quality','LD release date','LD video quality','production dates','LD audio noise','LD supplement','other works','LD analog right','LD quality of source','LD aspect ratio','other literature','LD video noise','mpaa') AND cct2.kind in ('crew','cast','complete+verified') AND it1.info not in ('runtimes','LD official retail price','LD review','mpaa','rentals','agent address','magazine cover photo','other works','LD frequency response','pictorial','alternate versions','LD disc format','nick names','LD dialogue intellegibility','certificates','bottom 10 rank','salary history','opening weekend','LD quality of source') AND t.production_year > 2010 AND (n.name like '%H%' OR n.name like '%M%' OR n.name like '%t%' OR n.name like '%N%') AND cct1.kind in ('cast','crew','complete') AND mi_idx.info > '4.0' AND (k.keyword like '%survival%' OR k.keyword like '%destiny%' OR k.keyword like '%prison%') AND mi.info in ('Hindi','Irish Gaelic','Romanian')
